    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nFind the value of x for the equation given log0.25x = 16.\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\n\u00a0log0.25x = 16\nIt can be write as\nx = (0.25)16\nx = (1/4)16\nx = 4-16",
